Class FullTimeStudent

  • java.lang.Object
    • SchoolMember
      • Student
        • FullTimeStudent
  • public class FullTimeStudent
extends Student
    This class represents a Full Time Student in a school. A full time student has to take a certain amount of extra credits apart from the base minimum credits for a student, i.e. the min credits for a full time student is more than a normal student.
    Version:
    8th September, 2018
